Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.31,0:00:13.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The Bog has already swallowed half of Kaiji's money—25 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:10.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すでに軍資金の半分2500万が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼にのみ込まれたカイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:15.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Still, he continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:18.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが つぎ込む\Nカイジ　ひたすらつぎ込む
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:18.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji continues intently!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:22.33,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\fad(550,550)\pos(640,505)}Iron Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:24.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Before he even notices it, Kaiji's wish, his prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:25.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつくとカイジの願い 悲願が…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:30.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドア…\N声に 言葉になる！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:26.59,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The door...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Escapes his lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Open! Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:35.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開け 開け 開け！ドア！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:35.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Open, door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:39.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開け！開かれろ！ドア！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:36.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:39.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Open up, door!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アラビアンナイトの\Nアリババと盗賊の話だっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:49.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's this supposed to be, the story of Ali Baba and the Forty Thieves?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:52.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,開けゴマとか抜かして\N開いた扉の向こうに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.03,0:00:55.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Do you really think you can open the door to fabulous riches just by shouting "open sesame?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:55.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金銀財宝の山が\Nあったっていうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:01:00.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし残念ながら\Nそんなことは おとぎ話の中の話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:01:00.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sadly for you, that kind of thing only happens in fairy tales.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.04,0:01:04.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In this world, there are no magic or miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:05.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありゃしねえんだよ\Nこの世には魔法も呪文も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そろそろ切り上げどころ\Nじゃないのかな？カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:08.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's it about time you just gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:15.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm certainly glad to take your money, but you're not doing yourself any good here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:11.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,散財してくれるのは ありがたいが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.44,0:01:15.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに空しく\Nカイジ君の金が消えるのも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:19.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for you, so I don't want to watch you force yourself into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:19.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふびんというか\Nさすがに忍びなくてね ハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ！あっ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:30.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And sadly, it doesn't matter how many you shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:30.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な？空しいだろ？\N何度打っても もう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:34.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　そうでもねえ\Nああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! That's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:37.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not wasting my time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:36.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空しくはねえ　ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.94,0:01:43.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,き… きとるのか？何か兆候が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.08,0:01:43.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Have you seen some kind of sign!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 実りつつある　ノックが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:47.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. My knocking's starting to get somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:57.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお！\N開く！開くぞ ドアが！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:56.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's opening! The door's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.49,0:02:00.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？ドアが開く？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:00.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The door's opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:04.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よし いけ！いけ！いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.69,0:02:03.22,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:10.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し　もう少しだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:10.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A little more! Just a little bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:14.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ？何をそんなに騒いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What? What's gotten into him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:17.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に変わったことは何も…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing's changed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:33.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた きた きた！\Nついにきたぞ クルーンに！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:33.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's made it to the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:36.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？な… 何だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.86,0:02:35.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.14,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's in the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.03,0:02:38.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入ったのか？クルーンに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wow, he made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとだ！入ってる！\Nどうやって？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:40.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How'd he do it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He went straight through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:43.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真っすぐだ　真っすぐ入った！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,村上！ど… どうしてだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:45.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Murakami! How'd he do it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:47.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,閉じるタイミングは\Nコンピューターが…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:47.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The flipper timing's supposed to be computer-controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:50.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ああ　て… 店長！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！何！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:57.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Impossible! They're not closing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:57.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな！\N閉じ切っていないじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.01,0:02:59.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガバガバだ　役をなしてない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The gap's too big! They can't block the balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:02.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're just helping it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ まるでザル
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きた きた\Nいけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:04.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:10.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ…\N水も漏らさぬ不可侵の砦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:13.74,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's going on!? That barrier's supposed to be impervious! Airtight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの鉄壁の門が閉まらないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.68,0:03:21.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yet it can't even close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これじゃ閉まるはずがない\Nダメだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:23.72,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It can't hold off anything anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この門では もう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の侵入 侵略を…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:27.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The enemy's attack— Their invasion—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:34.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's useless! It's smashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:34.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,防げない… 決壊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:37.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな　何だ これは\Nあり得ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why!? This is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:48.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ　それにしても こいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:51.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He thought up something unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:51.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とんでもないことを\N思いつきやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:59.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってんのか？敵はあの城門を\N自在にｺﾝﾋﾟｭｰﾀｰ制御できるんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:59.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You know those flippers are computer-controlled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さん　関係ないんすよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't care, Endoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:08.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how they control it if I crush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,制御もクソも　クラッシュ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:08.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっ壊しちまえばいいんですよ\N根本から
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっ壊す？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Crush them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明します　あの役モノは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here, I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The flippers are pushed by these shafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:15.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここの支柱が動いて\N開閉してるんです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:19.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ですから そこがヘタれば\N役をなさなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:19.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Bend them, and they won't close.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:22.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし ヘタると言っても…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:21.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And how are we supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We melt them, with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,溶かします　こいつで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:27.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？カイロ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:27.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A hand warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:32.23,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The second you break the vacuum seal on a disposable hand warmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:32.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　使い捨てカイロは\N真空パックの袋を破った瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:36.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空気に触れて鉄が酸化し\N熱の放射発生が始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:36.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,the iron inside begins to oxidize and produce heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:43.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We scale that down and hide it in the shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:39.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この原理を\Nそのままミニサイズにして
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:44.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなふうに\N役モノの支えの部分に仕込む
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:48.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But then we can't break the seal directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:48.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも仕込んだ真空パックの袋は\N直接 破ることはできないので
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんぺいとうのような\Nギザギザのある玉を
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:52.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need to sneak in balls covered in tiny spikes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隣に仕込んでおきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:58.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば役モノが動くたびに\N真空パックをノックし続け
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:57.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we do that, then every time I take a shot, it'll knock on the vacuum pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:00.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある回数を超えたら袋は破れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.00,0:05:04.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shoot enough times, and the iron will start to oxidize—it'll heat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:05.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鉄の酸化 すなわち\N熱が発生し始める
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:09.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And the shaft will melt from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.31,0:05:09.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結果 その支柱を内部から溶かす
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.18,0:05:13.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが少量だろ 中に仕込める鉄粉は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:13.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But we can't fit much iron powder in the shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 発生する熱も少量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:19.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't get all that hot. Will it be enough to melt the plastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:19.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもんで溶かせんのか？\N支柱のプラスチックを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:23.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっしゃる通りです\Nこの程度の熱では無理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're right. It won't be hot enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:28.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも変えればいいんです\N一部分でもいいから別の素材に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:28.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But change the material we're working with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:31.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I think this will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それには これが効果的です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:39.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… 何だ？それ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.98,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:42.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ？\Nサッカロイドの凝固形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:44.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Crystallized saccharide. That is, candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまりアメです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.02,0:05:47.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アメ？\N一部分とはいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:52.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we replace part of the shaft with a material which melts easily, it'll warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,熱に弱い素材を仕込めば\Nあの支えの部品はヘタる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:54.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかもそのヘタリは\N打ってすぐじゃなく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:56.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And it won't happen right after it's hit. It'll take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:57.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ある程度 時間を経た後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:01.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１時間ぐらいは打った後に\N壊れてくれないと困る
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:01.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We need it to take an hour or so of being hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:08.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Otherwise they'll pick up on it while testing the machine before we even show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:05.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でないと勝負前の試し打ちや\N俺たちが勝負に行く前に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かが打ち出してヘタったら\N話にならない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:13.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だがどうやって その仕掛けを\N仕込む？すり替える？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:12.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But how do we get it in? How do we swap them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:18.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの沼は24時間\N厳重に監視されてるんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:17.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They've got the Bog on camera 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:22.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに通常の状態では\N一分の隙もない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:21.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Normally, we'd have no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:25.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし何らかの理由で\N沼の部品が破損
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:25.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But what if the Bog's damaged for some reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:29.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしくは故障した時\N敵はどうすると思います？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:29.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What do you think they do when it breaks down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:33.87,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They send it to the manufacturer for repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:33.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,外部に注文するんですよ\N沼の製造元に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:37.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その工場が部品の修理を終え\Nカジノに納品するまで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:39.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's completely out of their hands until it comes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵はまったくノータッチ\N管轄外ってやつで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:43.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's out of their control! Their guard's down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,警戒ゼロ　ノーガード
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:49.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So let's not sweat the little things! Let's just smash the machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:49.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要するに細かい話は抜きで\N壊しちまえばいいんですよ 台を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And I know just the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:58.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幸いなことに約１名\N恨み骨髄　あの沼を叩き壊すに
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.65,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He holds enough of a grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:07:01.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He has plenty of reason to smash the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:01.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,十分な理由を持つ男を\N知っています
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:09.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We get him to smash the Bog, and have the parts swapped in by the repairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.99,0:07:05.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その男に台を壊させ\N修理を頼まれた工場が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:09.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新しい部品を納品する前に\Nすり替えておく
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:14.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前もって用意した\N時限破壊装置入りの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:15.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,These special self-destructing flippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このスペシャル役モノを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:19.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Think it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:19.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうです？いい計画でしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たぶん失敗するな それ\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:30.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:34.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき｢壊すのに十分な恨み｣って\N言ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:34.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You say he's got enough of a grudge to smash it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:37.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but it'll look pretty forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:38.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう その辺りからウソくせえ\Nプンプン臭うだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:41.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They'll think the whole thing stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何か納得のいかない空気 違和感が
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたって引っかかる\Nなんで壊すんだと？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They won't be able to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Why would he smash it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:48.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What would he be doing that for? Anger? Resentment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,壊して何になる？怒り 恨み
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.24,0:07:51.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those won't be enough to make him do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:51.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことで\Nこんな大それたことするか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:56.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'd have to have a different reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:56.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となると当然 何か別の理由が\Nあるんじゃないかと考える
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:59.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも遠藤さん\Nその違和感っていう引っかかり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:08:01.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can use that suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:02.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構 使えるんですよ\Nああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:07.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Remember, bones are strongest where they've broken before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:06.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うじゃないですか\N骨は折れてくっついたところが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一番 強くなるって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:12.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり うまく使えば\Nその違和感こそ強力な接着剤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:12.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we do this right, that suspicion will hold everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:16.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's the trick, the genius, of my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:16.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の仕事を仕上げる隠し味 妙趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,沼の大騒ぎが\Nさしたる疑いも呼ばず
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.90,0:08:23.76,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're worse off if we don't make a scene and just sit there taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スッと通過しちまったら\Nむしろ そっちのほうが怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:28.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時は感じずとも\N心の深い消化不良というか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:30.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If we don't, Ichijou's stomach will start to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:32.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くすぶり続けます　消えぬ疑念が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.04,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He'll begin to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:37.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So make a scene, and then he's relieved when it comes to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,むしろ一度疑わせ それを解決
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消化させてやるのが うまい手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:42.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフ　残念だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:46.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Did you find what you were looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:46.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で 見つかったかい？\Nお目当てのものは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:51.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We give him exactly what he was expecting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:52.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,与えてやればいい\N敵が納得のいく理由 解決を
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.82,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Is this what you were after?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが狙いだったんだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:01.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が頭が切れると\N思ってる奴ほど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:09:06.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He thinks he's clever. We can use that to trick him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:06.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この解決 消化の心理の穴\N仕組みにハマっちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This will take all the suspicion off us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:11.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心してください\N見事 脱臭してみせますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:14.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That "stink" you were talking about will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:15.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,遠藤さんが言うところの\Nウソ臭さを
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:19.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,脱臭か　大したもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Remove the stink, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:22.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You did a damn good job of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:22.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,消したんだな　見事 臭いを
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:27.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,And now you've got that nancy Ichijou off balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:28.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして出し抜いた\Nあの細心で用心深い一条を
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:32.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時間はかかったが第２関門も突破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:32.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It took a while, but the second gate's fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るはクルーン
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:33.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All that's left is the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:37.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのクルーンだけだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Nothing but the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:47.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ 言われずとも いくさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:49.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't even need to tell me! There's nowhere to go from here but up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:51.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで いかずにどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,This is a once-in-a-lifetime chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな千載一遇の…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わりか　３枚目も
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna quit after three cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ！いいところなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}It was just getting good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ続けるよな？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}You think he's gonna keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:06.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも もう3000万も使ってんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}He's gone through 30 mil already...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,{\bord6}I've still got twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるさ　まだ2000万
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すげえ！すげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:16.40,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Man, if I quit here I'd never forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然さ　ここでガス欠ってんじゃ\N泣いても泣き切れねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっと女神が\Nほほえんだってのによ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I can't let down Lady Luck now that she's smiling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:20.19,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:22.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ そうだ！\Nいけ いけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.19,0:10:22.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万だ　とりあえず\Nうっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Another 10 mil for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:28.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up, I'm gonna lose my flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:29.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっさとしな！グズグズされちゃ\N流れが切れる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:34.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て ここまでだ　勝負は中止！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:30.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No more! You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:36.55,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I won't let you buy any more Paqy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上のパッキーの購入は\N認めない！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:39.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はあ？\Nはあじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:43.68,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't just give me that blank stare! Everyone can see what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:43.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ろ　誰が見たって\Nもう続けられる状態じゃあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:45.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:48.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか？構わないぜ 俺は別に
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't really give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:50.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ… ふざけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:50.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't fuck around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:53.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to fuck around, it just comes naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:52.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふざけてなんかいないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,神様のおぼしめしで今\Nクルーンにフリーパス
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:56.38,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,God's just blessed me with a free pass to the trays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I need to take advantage of my good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この幸運を生かさないとな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:00.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… 貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:05.37,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ichijou. This kind of problem is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条　言っとくがな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:05.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この破損 アクシデントは\Nそっちのミス
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.27,0:11:09.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,責任 不備 関係ねえんだぜ\N打ち手の俺には
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:09.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't hate the player. Hate the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.94,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it say so right on that sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこの ただし書きにも\Nあるじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:20.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Once someone starts playing, nothing gets changed behind the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:15.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢一度 打ち始めたら\Nどんな不都合が起ころうとも｣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:18.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢ガラス戸を開けての\Nクギ調整等の操作｣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:22.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢変更はしない｣と\Nバカ！よく読んでみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.46,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Read the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:25.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,書いてあるだろうが！\N好きなだけ遊んでいいが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:28.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It says you can play as much as you like, only as long as you're not cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただしゴト行為があった場合は\N別だと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゴト？\Nとぼけるな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb! It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかじゃないか\N６日前の大暴れ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:37.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You swapped something in while the Bog was being repaired after you broke it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:38.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれでこの沼を壊し\N修理に出した部品をすり替えた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:41.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな細工か知らんが\N何かを仕組んだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:41.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you did it, but you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その偽物に！違うか！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:43.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's a fake! We both know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフ　何を言い出すと思ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.49,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of all the things for you to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臆測だろ　今言ったことすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're just guessing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…\N何一つないだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:57.02,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You have absolutely no proof that the old man or I did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺やおっちゃんが\Nそんなことしたって証拠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:12:00.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ 黙れ 黙れ！\N証拠もクソもあるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Shut up shut up shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't need any proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう考えるしかねえんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's gotta be what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:06.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,After you smashed it like that, anyone would be sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:05.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その壊れ方は\N誰がどう考えたって！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.70,0:12:09.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハ 一条　そんなのは通らない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:09.47,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Silly Ichijou. No one's going to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今やってるのは\N1000円 2000円じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:14.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're not playing for thousands. We're playing for millions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウン千万 億っていうギャンブルだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:18.88,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No one's going to stop a high-stakes game for that kind of guesswork.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:18.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな大勝負を不確かな臆測や\N決めつけで中止なんてできない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…\N第一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:27.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Plus, you've had these flippers rigged anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:25.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このクルーン前の門番に関しては\Nやってたよな？あんたら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.78,0:12:29.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いなく操作を\Nうっ… 何を言う！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:36.00,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,They're supposed to let one ball in three through, but how many have they stopped?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本来 ３分の１の確率で通る玉が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:36.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何回連続で この役モノに\N止められたと思ってる？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.83,0:12:38.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,200回は超えている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:42.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Over 200! Yet I've ignored it and kept playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:42.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし目をつぶってきただろ？\Nそのことについて俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…\N当然さ　仕方ないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.52,0:12:45.99,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't even care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Because I don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:49.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって証拠がないんだもんな\N証拠が
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:51.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら黙るしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:54.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I just shut up. Because I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.31,0:12:55.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが真剣勝負ってもんだろ\Nぐっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:59.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But here you are, letting people play when things go your way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:59.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを自分に都合のいい時は\N続行させておいて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:04.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,and then shutting them down the second something you don't expect happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.18,0:13:04.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かハプニング 不測の事態で\N都合が悪くなると中止なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:07.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No one's gonna put up with that self-centered bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,通るかよ！そんな自分勝手が！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:10.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろ？みんな\Nおお
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ！\Nその通りだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:11.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:12.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can see right through you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見え見えだったぞ！\Nやらせろ！やらせろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:15.81,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let him play!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He's playing the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ… こいつら調子に乗って…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:20.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,て… 店長　電話ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss! Phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for that right now! Tell him to call back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:23.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ！こんな時に！切れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.31,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,し… しかし…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:29.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichijou speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　一条ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Just what is going on up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんだ 一体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おっ 誰だ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:34.92,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Who's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:40.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王国 王国帝愛グループの\N幹部候補生ともあろう者が
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:42.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I never expected this kind of behavior from a man tapped to join Teiai Group's management.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:45.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんたる醜態だ\Nああ… まさか その声は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.25,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.39,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hyodo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵藤さま！\N何？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:48.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:51.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 会長　一体…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir, what can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:56.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've seen how powerless you are, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ていた　一部始終を
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:57.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,力足らずが
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:13:59.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Would you like to sleep with the fishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:14:00.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,入るか？海に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:05.01,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Rot at the bottom of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,深海に漂う藻くず よどみ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会長…\Nはっ クズが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:16.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お恥ずかしいところをお見せして\N申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.62,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry you had to see that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Take this bet, Ichijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:19.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一条　受けてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うーん　確かに奴が\Nその真ん中の役モノに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:28.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,He may well have done something to the flippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:28.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かを仕組んだのは明らかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:32.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 台を開け\Nその部分を入念に調べれば
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:36.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you take apart the machine and go digging, you might a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:36.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かタネのようなものが\N出てくるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But that'd be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:40.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし そこまで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのことと奴を結びつけるものが\Nとりあえずない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.24,0:14:44.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to tie him to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:48.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とすると奴のゴトと\N断定することはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:48.36,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So you can't prove he's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:54.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's obvious that someone's cheating, so you can stop the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:53.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも何者かによるゴト行為が\N発生したことは確かだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中止 勝負取りやめということも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:59.61,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You can force him to stop, if you really want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強引ながら できないこともない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　ですから会長…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.61,0:15:01.57,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course! So, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:05.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし それはこちらに\N失点がない場合に限る
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.57,0:15:06.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,But only when we don't lose anything by doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ？\N下手クソが　なんて下手なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:09.93,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You're such a fuckup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見え見えじゃないか\Nお前の遠隔操作 ブロック
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:14.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've been watching your "block" and it's completely obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:25.15,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,With that kind of unfair trick going on, there's no way you can stop him playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:20.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな下手クソな不公平感が\N吹き上がる見せ物をしていて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:25.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分に不利な状況になったから\N中止などと言えるわけもあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:31.91,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You don't need to be fair, but you need to look fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:28.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,公平である必要はないが\N少なくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:32.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,公平感は客に与えねばならんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:36.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日のお前の始末 やり方は下の下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:36.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Your performance today is the poorest I've seen in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなやり方では
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:42.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,At that rate, you'll never wring enough money out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:42.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,搾り取れんだろうが 下民どもから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ！す… すいません！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.67,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:50.69,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So you need to let him play, so it doesn't look unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから受けてやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:50.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上 客に不公平感を\N持たせてはいかん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことをすれば\N沼だけの問題では済まず
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:58.43,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,If you cut him off, it'll reflect poorly on the casino and the whole of Teiai, not just the Bog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:58.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カジノ全体 帝愛そのものへの\N不信感につながる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.35,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You mustn't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけは絶対に避けねばならん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:03.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帝愛は愛されねばならんのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:06.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Teiai must be well-loved to keep the cash flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:06.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっともっと金を得るために
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:09.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… はい！\Nだから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:15.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So we have to let Kaiji finish himself off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここは潔くカイジの言い分を認め\Nその上で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:18.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺せばよい　魔性３段クルーンで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:18.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,In the Demonic Triple Tray...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うう…\Nそれとも自信がないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:23.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or don't you have the trays rigged?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:24.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーン勝負\Nいえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.24,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I do, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:27.30,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I thought those were your best work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:27.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは\Nお前の自信作ではなかったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:31.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じられんのか？\N自分を 自分自身を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:31.83,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Can't you believe in yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ！そんなことはありません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:38.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,That's not it, sir! The trays are impenetrable! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:38.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンは絶対です\N上りません！水は決して上へ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:41.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フフフ　そうだ その意気だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Excellent. That's what I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:45.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦え　そして勝て
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.29,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Fight and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:47.48,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:48.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは死ね\Nえっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハ　万が一の場合はな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:52.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't expect that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,て… 店長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:06.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Those trays went untouched!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンは… あのクルーンは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:07.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手つかずのはず
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:12.66,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All he smashed were the flippers in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:10.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この間の大暴れで破壊されたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真ん中の役モノだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンは手つかず\N交換もされてない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:16.26,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The trays were untouched! They didn't get replaced!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい 村上\Nあっ はい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey, Murakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.73,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例の役モノを交換する時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:25.77,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,You were there when they swapped out the flippers, right? {consistency!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 ついていたよな？\Nええ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:26.90,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その時 何か怪しい動きが\Nなかったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:29.86,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did anything seem strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:33.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Did the repairman do anything to the trays?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:32.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その作業員がクルーンに\N何か仕掛けるような
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:36.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ　クルーンには\N指一本 触れさせていません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:36.28,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,No, sir! He didn't even touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:43.27,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I checked them afterwards while I was testing it, and they were fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:41.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに交換の後 試し打ちと共に\Nクルーンのチェックもしましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,異常は認められませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:46.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目もか？\Nもちろんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The third tray too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:48.79,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Of course! I really put that one through its paces!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:49.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,３段目は特に入念にチェック
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:55.41,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I tried with dozens of balls, and none made it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:52.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10 20と玉を入れ試しましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:56.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当たりは皆無\N何の問題もありません
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.85,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Good. Then there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか　なら問題ない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:03.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,As long as the trays are untouched, we can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:03.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーンに変化がない以上\N敗北はない！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.56,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:06.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいおい！一体いつまで\N待たせるつもりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:07.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna keep us waiting!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:09.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　さっさと始めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.03,0:18:09.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's get this started!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:13.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,再開しろ 再開！\Nそうだ そうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:11.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.84,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:17.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりました\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.03,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:21.58,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We would never get in the way of a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:21.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご安心ください　当カジノは\N逃げも隠れもいたしません
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:26.44,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can see the terrible condition the machine's in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:24.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご覧のように台は壊滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:28.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどい惨状でありますが\Nこの状態を引き起こしたのが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:32.09,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but I have no proof that Kaiji, the player, is behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:32.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打ち手のカイジ君である確証が\Nない以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:35.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,認めます　彼の続行を\Nおお！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:35.10,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I'll let him continue playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やった！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:36.63,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:42.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,村上\Nはっ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:41.64,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Murakami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:42.70,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は通常設定だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Today's setting is normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.60,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:50.21,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It's set to 5-5-5.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プラス５５５で\Nセットしておりますが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:53.51,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Change it to 7-7-7. Just to be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,念のため７７７にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:56.13,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can't let him hit the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,万が一にも突破は許されない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.16,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:01.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺す！ここでカイジを殺す！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:01.89,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1000万パッキー\Nあと こいつが２枚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.95,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Ten million Paqy... I've got two of these left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:16.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I've got to do it with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:16.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決まる　どうであれ これで
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.52,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.69,0:19:20.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぜ！\Nおお！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:37.11,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All that's left is their last line of defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:38.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残るは敵の本丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.97,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All that's left is the trays!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:41.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このクルーンだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:44.53,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It may be an impenetrable fortress,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:44.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,難攻不落　鉄壁の城だが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.54,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,but I have air superiority!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,制空権は奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:50.05,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,All they can do is look up at the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:50.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,空を見上げるだけさ 敵は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.50,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,So I'll make it rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:53.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となりゃ降らせてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:56.80,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,A rain of silver balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:57.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雨 銀玉の雨を！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:03.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,爆撃だ！焼く　焼き尽くす！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:19:58.96,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll bomb them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.34,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,I'll burn them! Burn them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:06.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ　第２関門も突破
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji breaks through the second gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.11,0:20:10.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次なる難関 ３段クルーンは\Nさらに強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:10.32,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,The next foe, the triple tray, is even fiercer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命を懸けた死の攻防
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.75,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Kaiji and Ichijou stake their lives on this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:16.78,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,Their battle continues beyond reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.92,0:20:16.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,狂気の限界を超え 戦いは続く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:18.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続く！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.08,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,It continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:41.12,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We can use that suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:50.18,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We're worse off if we don't make a scene and just sit there taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:57.07,kaiji-dialog,,0,0,0,,We give him exactly what he was expecting!
